        </div>
        <div class=" wow fadeInUp " data-wow-delay="1.0s">
          <p class="align">Email is notorious for being one of the least secure methods of communication across the internet. Email compromises are extremely common, and nearly all email providers such as Gmail and Outlook are scanning and accessing content held within emails. Zebu uses military grade encryption across the entire platform to protect your team's work. End-to-end, no knowledge encryption solution ensures that no one (not even us), nor the government or hackers can get your data.</p>
